About
=====

Lightweight and easy-to-deploy TCP chatting server. It was mainly designed for small communities but doesn't lack anything regarding security.

Protocol
========

`ax` uses a highly understandable and simple protocol I've came up with. See below for examples.

class Payload:
    message: str
    args: list[str]

Example `payload.message`: INCOMING_MESSAGE
Example `payload.args`: [<author>, <content>]

Client-side payloads
====================

NICK|<desired_nick>
LIST
WHOAMI

Server-side payloads
====================

SLOW_DOWN
UNAUTHORIZED
INCOMING_MESSAGE|<author>|<message>
PING

NICK_ALREADY_SET
NICK_INVALID
NICK_TAKEN

NICK_OK|<desired_nick>
LIST_OK|<user1>|<user2>|<user3>|...
WHOAMI_OK|<nick>
